Uses of Package
de.mslab.diffbuilder

  • Packages that use de.mslab.diffbuilder 
    Package Description
    de.mslab.bicliquesearch
    Provides classes which implement the biclique finding process.
    de.mslab.diffbuilder
    Provides helper classes which are required for biclique creation, such as to construct differences for bit-wise or byte-wise operating ciphers, or to compare differentials for their independency.
  • Classes in de.mslab.diffbuilder used by de.mslab.bicliquesearch 
    Class and Description
    DifferenceBuilder
    A value builder computes in increasing manner all n-bit/n-byte values with less or equal a maximum number of '1' bits/bytes.
  • Classes in de.mslab.diffbuilder used by de.mslab.diffbuilder 
    Class and Description
    AbstractDifferenceIterator 
    BitwiseDifferenceBuilder
    Computes in increasing manner all n-bit values with less or equal a maximum number of '1' bit, while all other bits are zero.
    BytewiseDifferenceBuilder 
    DifferenceBuilder
    A value builder computes in increasing manner all n-bit/n-byte values with less or equal a maximum number of '1' bits/bytes.
    DifferenceIterator 
    NibblewiseDifferenceBuilder
    Computes in increasing manner all n-byte values with less or equal a maximum number of '1' bytes, while all other bytes are zero.
